ğŸ§± 3. Database Schema Design (ERD Overview)

Entities & Relationships:

[Flight] â†â”€â”€ (Many) â”€â”€â”€ [Booking] â†â”€â”€ (One) â”€â”€â”€ [Payment]

One Flight can be booked in many Bookings

One Booking has one Payment



